TITLE: Client WebSocket Connection and Conversation (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code establishes a WebSocket connection to a server using `tgrid` and initiates a conversation using the `AgenticaRpcService`. It defines a WebSocketConnector with handlers for 'text' and 'describe' events, logs the received role and text or description and connects to the server. Then, gets a driver for the `AgenticaRpcService` to start the conversation.
