TITLE: Expected API Call Sequence
DESCRIPTION: This JSON defines the expected sequence of API calls to fulfill the user's request. It lists operations for displaying sales, retrieving product details, creating orders, and publishing orders, including descriptions and parameters of each operation. The operations are designed to simulate a real-world e-commerce interaction with an A.I. agent.
