TITLE: Expected API Calls for Macbook Order
DESCRIPTION: This JSON payload represents the expected sequence of API calls that an AI agent should perform to fulfill a user's request to view sales, retrieve Macbook details, add to cart, and publish the order. It describes operations to list summarized sales, fetch detailed sale information, create an order, and publish the order.
