DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code snippet demonstrates how to initialize an Agentica agent with the GoogleImageService connector and OpenAI's GPT model. It utilizes typia for type safety and dotenv for managing environment variables.
SOURCE: https://github.com/wrtnlabs/agentica/blob/main/website/content/tutorial/productivity/google-image.mdx#_snippet_1

