TITLE: Testing a GET Request and Generating REST Docs in Kotlin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates testing a GET request to retrieve a sample by ID using MockMvc. It performs the request, validates the HTTP status and JSON response, and generates REST Docs documentation using MockMvcRestDocumentationWrapper.document. The documentation includes request and response details.
