DESCRIPTION: This snippet validates the input for deleting an existing Bbs article. The main validation is that the article ID is present and in the correct UUID format, checked via typia's `isFormatUuid` function.  If the ID is valid the function returns a success boolean and the input data; otherwise, it will return a list of errors.
