TITLE: Creating API Documentation with Swagger Annotations (PHP)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to define API documentation within a PHP Laravel controller using Swagger annotations. It showcases the use of `@OA` tags to describe the API endpoint, request body, and response formats.  The example defines a `POST` endpoint `/boards` with request body parameters for title, content and files.
